description: Are you interested in what happened on this day? With On This Day you get the most important world events that happened on this day for every day of the year. Information source: Wikipedia.org.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask On This Day to get on this day for today.
Alexa, ask On This Day to get on this day for August seventeenth.
